data.description: If you're looking for the perfect home in SW Cape Coral, look no further! This beautiful home boasts an oversized corner lot and plenty of curb appeal. Step inside through the elegant French doors and be greeted by the grand foyer and tray ceilings. The open floor plan provides an easy flow through the home, allowing an abundance of natural light. You'll love the 12x24 tile throughout - no more worries with carpet! The kitchen is truly a chef's dream w/ beautiful level 4 granite countertops, HUGE island, white shaker cabinets, and stainless steel appliances. With 3 bedrooms plus a den, there is ample space to accommodate a growing family or guests. The yard is a blank slate waiting for you to make it your own. You can fit a pool for those hot summer days or let your furry friends roam free in the backyard- it's fenced in for their protection! With quick access to Veterans and Pine Island Road, you'll be close to plenty of shopping, scrumptious restaurants, and even golf courses. Don't hesitate...make this your forever home today!
